CHANGES IN VERSION 1.99.0
-------------------------
 o Methods rtime, tic, ionCount, polarity and acquisitionNum implemented <2016-05-25 Wed>.
 o Documentation added for most methods <2016-05-25 Wed>.
 o Methods peaksCount and spectra for OnDiskMSnExp objects implemented <2016-05-24 Tue>.
 o Performance and validation tests for the Spectrum1 C-constructor <2016-05-23 Mon>.
 o Spectrum1 constructor implemented in C (presently not exported) <2016-05-20>
 o length, scanIndex, acquisitionNum and centroided implemented <2016-05-20>
 o Implemented fromFile and msLevel for OnDiskMSnExp <2016-05-19 Thu>
 o Implemented an OnDiskMSnExp class for on-the-fly data import <2016-05-19 Thu>
 o Fixed the validate method for pSet to play nicely with OnDiskMSnExp objects
   <2016-05-19 Thu>
 o Added slot onDisk to pSet objects (TRUE for OnDiskMSnExp objects, FALSE otherwise).
   The getter method isOnDisk checks for the presence of the slot in the object
   (backward compatibility) <2016-05-19 Thu>
 o Implemented a ProcessingStep class that helps to keep track how (spectra) data
   should be processed on the fly <2016-05-18 Wed>
